| HistoryText             = The Moth Squadron was a team of [[Strategic Homeland Intervention, Enforcement and Logistics Division (Earth-616)|S.H.I.E.L.D.]] agents led by [[Daisy Johnson (Earth-616)|Quake (Agent Daisy Johnson)]] and including [[Ellis Love (Earth-616)|Agent Ellis Love]], [[Elena Rodríguez (Earth-616)|Slingshot (Yo-Yo Rodriguez)]], [[Cornell Gray (Earth-616)|"Grey"/Agent Cornell Gray]], [[Agent Kellam (Earth-616)|Agent Kellam]] and a sixth unnamed agent.

Together, they monitored the [[Inhumans (Inhomo supremis)|Inhuman]] city of [[New Attilan]].{{r|Secret Warriors Vol 2 1}}

While on this assignment, they were re-dispatched by [[Steven Rogers (Earth-61311)|Captain America]] (secretly leader of [[Hydra (Earth-616)|Hydra]]) to [[Inner Harbor|Baltimore Harbor]], to investigate a base, where they were ambushed by the [[Wrecking Crew (Earth-616)|Wrecking Crew]]. They were all killed in the brawl, save for Quake.{{r|Secret Warriors Vol 2 1}}

Half of S.H.I.E.L.D. D.C. offices were dispatched on the site to retrieve the bodies and investigate.{{r|Secret Warriors Vol 2 1}}
